417. Neth J Med. 2012 Oct;70(8):357-64.

Which long-acting bronchodilator is most cost-effective for the treatment of 
COPD?

Hoogendoorn M(1), Kappelhoff BS, Overbeek JA, Wouters EF, Rutten-van Mölken MP.
